          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>In 2019, DZHUS won the Cruelty-free Fashion prize at Best Fashion Awards - the most prestigious fashion rating in Ukraine, and in 2021, DZHUS’ eco project, “Unpacking”, was awarded a special prize at Fashion Film Festival Kyiv. Short-listed for the International Woolmark Prize back in 2015, DZHUS presents seasonal collections during Ukrainian and Paris Fashion Weeks.</p>",
